Package org.aludratest.config

Interface Summary
AludraTestConfig Provides the central configuration of AludraTest.
Configurable Interface for classes which instances can be configured using the published AludraTest configuration mechanism.
Configurator Interface for objects being able to configure Configurable objects.
MutablePreferences Interface for configuration Preferences objects which can be modified.
Preferences The basic interface for configuration data.
 

Class Summary
ComponentConfigurator Helper class and entry point to AludraTest Configuration Service.
ValidatingPreferencesWrapper Helper class for Preferences consumers which can be used to have getter methods which validate the existence of a configuration property when trying to retrieve it.
 

Exception Summary
ConfigurationException  
 

Annotation Types Summary
ConfigNodeProperties  
ConfigNodeProperty  
ConfigProperties Tool annotation to use multiple ConfigProperty annotations for one type.
ConfigProperty Describes a configuration property used by the annotated service interface or implementation.
InternalComponent This annotation marks a component or service interface as "internal".
